# Project Rules (Agents)

This is a collaborative vertical-slice project for the LOS Hackathon.

## Vertical Slices
- **Notes Domain (Groovster):**
  - Model: `Note`
  - Logic: `src/lib/tools/notes.ts`
  - UI: `src/components/notes-list.tsx`
  - Refer to `GROOVSTER.md` for full specs.

- **Tasks Domain (Okkio):**
  - Model: `Task`
  - Logic: `src/lib/tools/tasks.ts`
  - UI: `src/components/tasks-list.tsx`
  - Refer to `OKKIO.md` for full specs.

## Shared Infrastructure
- API: `src/app/api/chat/route.ts`
- UI: `src/components/chat-interface.tsx`
- DB: `src/lib/db.ts`

Follow the role-specific instructions in `GROOVSTER.md` and `OKKIO.md` to avoid domain overlap.
